NOTICE - Trezoa SDK
===================

This project contains software originally developed by the Solana Foundation
and various contributors, which has been modified and adapted for the Trezoa
Blockchain ecosystem.

ORIGINAL SOFTWARE:
- Name: solana-sdk
- Version: v1.18.26
- Source: https://crates.io/crates/solana-sdk
- License: Apache License 2.0

MODIFICATIONS:
This software has been modified by the TRZ Ledger Foundation to:
- Rebrand from Solana to Trezoa
- Update naming conventions (SOL → TRZ, SPL → TPL)
- Adapt for Trezoa blockchain compatibility
- Add Trezoa-specific functionality

